# Styling Conventions

## Tailwind Variants (`tv`)

All component styling uses `tv()` with named slots. No inline className strings on components.

## Theme Tokens (`@theme` in `index.css`)

- **Fonts**: `font-display` (Oswald), `font-body` (DM Sans)
- **Colors**: `accent`, `accent-secondary`, `surface`, `surface-elevated`, `text-bright`, `text-muted`, `warm`
- **Shadows**: `shadow-stage-card`
- **Sizing**: `max-w-content` via `--container-content`
- **Glow utilities**: `stage-glow`, `stage-glow-strong`

## Responsive

- Mobile-first: base = mobile, override at `lg:` only.
- Document scroll (Lenis); sections use `min-h-dvh` where needed.
